\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">后置节点：可以连接除导入以外的任意可连接的节点</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">注意事项</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">请输入所有的必填参数</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">参数说明</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（1）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、选择对应的数据源</span>\\数据源类型，可获取对应的结果数据</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、可进行循环抓取的配置</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（3）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、带星号的为必填参数，请务必输入</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（4）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、当数据抓取连接数据抓取时，右侧的参数设置会变动</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">输出结果</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">按照数据抓取的参数设置抓取对应的结果数据</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <br/>\r\n</p>' WHERE (`type_no`='dataCrawl');
