t-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">后置节点：可以连接任意可连接的节点</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">注意事项</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">对文件的格式有要求</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">参数说明</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（1）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、原字段为导入文件中的表头的字段</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、现字段为所选择数据源类型的存储字段</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">输出结果</span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">\r\n    <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">经过字段表头匹配的数据，未选择匹配的不被输出</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <br/>\r\n</p>' WHERE (`type_no`='dataImport');
